      <div class="modal__container" role="dialog" aria-modal="true" aria-labelledby="modal-1-title">
        <header class="modal__header">
          <h2 id="modal-1-title" class="modal__title">
            Guide to install this Progressive Web App
          </h2>
          <button class="modal__close" aria-label="Close modal" data-micromodal-close></button>
        </header>
        <main class="modal__content" id="modal-1-content">
          <h3>Installation guide for iOS</h3>
          <ol>
            <li>Open <a href="https://detoxify.app">https://detoxify.app</a> on Safari. Other browsers, such as Chrome, won’t work for this.</li>
            <li>Search and find the app that you’re addicted to.</li>
            <li>Once you opened, tap the Share button at the bottom of the page.</li>
            <li>In the lowest row, scroll until you see “Add to Home Screen” and tap this.</li>
            <li>Choose a name for the app on your home screen and press on “Add” to add the app on your home screen.</li>
            <li>Remove the real app that you’re addicted to (if you are brave enough)</li>
            <li>Now next time when you open the app, you’ll see the detoxified version.</li>
          </ol>
          <h3>Installation guide for Android</h3>
          <ol>
            <li>Open <a href="https://detoxify.app">https://detoxify.app</a> on Chrome (or any other Chromium based browser such as Brave).</li>
            <li>Click on the "Install" button</li>
            <li>Click "Add" on the pop-up</li>
            <li>Wait a few seconds until it installs, the app will then appear in your app drawer</li>
            <li>Remove the real app that you’re addicted to (if you are brave enough)</li>
            <li>Now next time when you open the app, you’ll see the detoxified version.</li>
          </ol>
        </main>
